{
  "stem": "2002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said to me that the wife is bringin' out coffee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But before she came with the coffee, the half a loaf of bread was gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Just with the saliva I swallowed it down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When he saw me, he felt so bad that for lunch he gave me another half a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after I worked for this man a certain time, than I went to work to-- to another gentleman who was the alcoholic.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was working, because he was makin' caskets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- and he was a genius of a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He could do anything, but he was an alcoholic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I worked for him a certain time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before you know, then I went for peddling also.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the war broke out, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was 1939.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You mentioned-- let's, before we talk about the war, you mentioned that the anti-Semitism in the towns would stop you--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from going to a certain school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very extreme.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For an example, there would be a guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would walk on the sidewalk, and-- and his elbow would totally stick out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If a Jew would pass, he would just hit him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was goin' on constantly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could go tell the police, it didn't mean nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One time I passed by, I see [? about ?] three guys beating up one guy-- beating him up only for one reason.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I [? mixed in ?] I went in to-- to help him out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I helped him out, and I walked away, you could even see it, maybe, if you look close, and I felt a knife in my-- in my face.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I turned around, one guy hit me with a knife on the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
